des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your “Kilo Plus”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “Afloia Home” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our “Afloia Home” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Enable “Afloia Home” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Afloia Home” login page;
(4) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(5) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the air purifier”
“Alexa, turn off the air purifier”
”Alexa, turn on the light”
“Alexa, turn off the light”
“Alexa, turn up the air purifier fan speed”
“Alexa, turn down the air purifier fan speed”
